### Customizing your theme
By default, Tailwind provides four `flex` utilities. You can customize these values by editing `theme.flex` or `theme.extend.flex` in your `tailwind.config.js` file.

```diff-js
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      flex: {
